reviewText: The tape was no good. It would not work. I will not be ordering any more and I don't like wasting time to write this.

Video was in good condition and shipped quickly.  These are getting harder to find.  WIsh someone would release them in DVD form, but until then, good to know that there is somewhere I can get it if I need it!  This is my third purchase of this VHS, I have worn out the first two.  Nice that is is a double,containing two shows, value for my buck.  I am an Activity Director at a nursing home.
